rows.label: qst711002_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh! This is wonderful!
It looks perfect!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0002
rows.name: Let me have a wee taste...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0003
rows.name: What's this?

rows.label: qst711002_msg0004
rows.name:
A mouth-watering medley of meat and
fish, stewed in a slightly sweet sauce...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0005
rows.name: This is some top-notch cooking!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0006
rows.name: ...But!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0007
rows.name:
I can tell you right now that this
is NOT Chilsainian cuisine!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0008
rows.name: And I'll tell you for why...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0009
rows.name: It's just too delicious!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0010
rows.name:
My mother's home-cooked recipes
never tasted as good as this!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0011
rows.name:
The smell of the fish was completely
overpowering, and the meat was tough
as old boots!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0012
rows.name:
That's the kind of poor quality you
can expect from Superbian cooking!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0013
rows.name:
If only there were someone who could
recreate that authentic local flavor...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0014
rows.name:
I doubt anyone but a true Superbian
can really prepare something that
appeals to our particular tastes.

rows.label: qst711002_msg0015
rows.name:
Ohh, what I wouldn't give for some
real Chilsainian Kascha...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0016
rows.name:
But whoever made this must have
some miraculous cooking skills!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0017
rows.name:
Do you think you could try it
with this recipe next?

rows.label: qst711002_msg0018
rows.name:
You should be able to capture that
distinctly acrid Superbian flavor!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0019
rows.name: Thanks very much! Can't wait!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0101
rows.name:
I doubt anyone but a true Superbian
can really prepare something that
appeals to our particular tastes.

rows.label: qst711002_msg0102
rows.name:
Ohh, what I wouldn't give for some
real Chilsainian Kascha...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0201
rows.name:
So, could you do it? Did you
cook some Superbian food?

rows.label: qst711002_msg0202
rows.name: This is...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0203
rows.name:
This food looks so good it
could satisfy any appetite!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0204
rows.name:
Well, the proof of the pudding is
in the tasting, as they say, so excuse
me while I tuck in...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0205
rows.name: Huh?!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0206
rows.name: Ermmmmmmm...

rows.label: qst711002_msg0207
rows.name: Rubbish!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0208
rows.name: This...taste!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0209
rows.name:
The spices are completely
overpowering so I can't tell
what I'm eating!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0210
rows.name:
The lentils have been boiled dry
and crunchy!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0211
rows.name:
Completely disgusting and inedible!
The quintessential Superbian cooking,
you might say!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0212
rows.name:
Well, I say disgusting, but there's
a certain charm to it that you can't
capture anywhere else.

rows.label: qst711002_msg0213
rows.name:
Yeah, in my hometown, there wasn't
anyone who could do Superbian cooking
as bad as this except my mother.

rows.label: qst711002_msg0214
rows.name:
Hey, why's that young Blady lady
looking at me with daggers?

rows.label: qst711002_msg0215
rows.name:
Anyway, you have all been so
kind to me!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0216
rows.name:
When you're in Superbia, you're
welcome to visit my house any time!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0217
rows.name:
I'll treat you to some proper
authentic Superbian food. Hahaha!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0301
rows.name:
I'm sorry, but delicious Superbian
cooking just isn't real Superbian
cooking!

rows.label: qst711002_msg0302
rows.name:
The taste has to be rubbish!
That's just the way I remember it
and the way it has to be!
